	   <tr><td colspan=2>Leave kiting to the druids and wizards please, its much easier just to send in the pet , dot the hg , heal your pet , blast the hg, heal heal heal , then redo dots till its dead<br> Kiting is for the people with snare<br>&nbsp;<br>Delvien Runecaster<br>Terris-Thule<br>Gnomer of the arts</td></tr>
