	   <tr><td colspan=2>Look around for a Screaming Mace.  You should be able to pick one up for fairly cheap (10-30pp).  The proc on it is &quot;Burst of Strength&quot; which jumps up the damage you do on the baddies for a short time.  Cast a DEX spell on yourself beforehand and you will be all set to crush skulls.  <br><br>Eventually you can look to upgrade to a more specialized weapon, but a Screamer will last you till L20.<br><br>--Pusbag Infection<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
