	   <tr><td colspan=2>Don't forget that you can access hotkeys via keyboard.  This becomes all important if you fight mobs that blind you ( reavers in CoM come to mind), or in duelling.  Have a hotkey<br>/target yournamehere<br>/cast X (cureblindness slot)<br>now if your screen goes black all you need to do is hit your hotkey number on the keyboard, and viola, you are cured.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec  4 10:11:40 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Shamu Whitewale<br>44 bar shm Xev</td></tr>
